Simple text format:

PROJECT:
Title
One sentence "pitch" description
What you'll do (single paragraph summary of what the project involves) 
Who can take part? (group size, ages, criteria)
What do young people get to do? (specific role descriptions)
When does it happen? (start / end dates, hours per session, frequency, duration)
Where?
Tags

HOST ORGANISATION
Host name
Host website
Host description
Key contact name / contact details

Checklist
- We have clearly defined volunteer roles (X)
- We have appropriate safeguarding policy in place (X)
- Our staff or adult volunteers are DBS checked (X)
- We can provide all necessary safety equipment to take part (X)
